{
  "stem": "18397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Jew couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I grow up in meantime, and I see what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No jobs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can have a job maybe to be something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it's not the job, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I decided myself-- because it was you had to finish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The rest wasn't so important by-- by a Jew, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Vilna, we had a technical school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was famous in the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they paid for it, for the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] From-- they were [INAUDIBLE] like to the [INAUDIBLE] or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I finished that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had to go to the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father wanted me to go over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the price was the same almost every place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I-- I decide I'll go to the technical school, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I was-- but I was there three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I got a job right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a job in-- what was it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they used to call it, a famous radio factory in the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got the job there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was your job?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I became a technician over there, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I knew everything, you know, mechanical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I went to work for another job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked two jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it wasn't hard for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what it was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was enjoying it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the meantime, I had two jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I used to make money from both sides.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I live in the big house, you know, in the big house in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had an elevator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the second elevator [LAUGHS] [INAUDIBLE] in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first one was belonged to the transportation employment, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
